skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: beta counter
des:
Let Alexa count for you!

Just say "Beta Counter, count to seven" and you will her Alexa counting from one to seven.
You can also specify the start number by saying "Beta Counter, count from four to nine".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
